message:

      |          ^~~~~~
helloworld.c:5:1: note: ‘stdout’ is defined in header ‘<stdio.h>’; did you forget to ‘#include <stdio.h>’?
    4 | #include <stdio.h>
  +++ |+#include <stdio.h>
    5 | 
helloworld.c:11:10: note: each undeclared identifier is reported only once for each function it appears in
   11 |     write(stdout, buffer, count);
      |          ^~~~~~
